flowRoot.flowPara: Found a bug? Report it! You can use the webpage or "reportbug" tool.
Say "yes" at install time. It will help to choose packages for the first CD/DVD and to assess user-base for any package

Write a manual, news, book or other materials that can help new users.

Adopt an orphaned package or start a packaging with a new software, alone or by joing in a team.
Read the technical documentation in the Developers' Corner, like New Maintainers' Guide, Debian Policy Manual or Debian Developer's Reference.

flowRoot.flowPara: Conservancy must move to a Supporter-driven organization so we can focus on critical free software issues that nobody else is tackling. Stand up for the GPL, support great member projects, and make your voice heard in support of free software. Donate today!
